Drop it.

607
00:43:49,800 --> 00:43:50,789
- Tired?
- Yeah.

608
00:43:50,960 --> 00:43:53,554
I'm not tired, are you?
No, you're not.

609
00:43:53,920 --> 00:43:55,911
So, shut up!

610
00:43:58,040 --> 00:44:00,474
Get up.
Yeah get up, now!

611
00:44:03,920 --> 00:44:06,070
- Got a smoke?
- I don't smoke.

612
