and bleeding.

687
00:49:15,680 --> 00:49:17,716
OK, good.
May I call you Jean-Claude?

688
00:49:18,760 --> 00:49:19,954
I'm Commissioner Bruges.

689
00:49:20,720 --> 00:49:22,233
You can call me Christian.

690
00:49:23,560 --> 00:49:25,755
