ask the good guys to come in

704
00:50:18,560 --> 00:50:20,755
naked, so they know
they're clean.

705
00:50:21,600 --> 00:50:22,953
How about naked?

706
00:50:29,040 --> 00:50:30,109
Fine, tell them.

707
00:50:54,560 --> 00:50:55,390
Where's Petrucciani?

708
00:50:57,880 --> 00:50:59,279
3. Stone falls on Egg,

