Hello!
Crank it up...

729
00:52:10,920 --> 00:52:13,150
Hey, man! You're breaking
up here, I'm losing you.

730
00:52:13,880 --> 00:52:15,757
You must be in a
tunnel or something!

731
00:52:16,000 --> 00:52:18,034
Cut the bullshit!
Come on the phone!

732
00:52:19,258 --> 00:52:20,690
All right.
Yeah, yeah.

733
00:52:21,320 --> 00:52:22,355
