752
00:53:27,920 --> 00:53:30,514
Close your eyes,
but let me talk to you.

753
00:53:30,680 --> 00:53:33,956
Anyway, when I see
you on screen,

754
00:53:34,120 --> 00:53:36,759
well, you're really
different!

755
00:53:36,920 --> 00:53:37,591
